### ============================================================
### 이벤트 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 현재 진행중인 이벤트 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/current
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ko

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 현재 진행중 또는 예정된 이벤트 목록 조회 (Home 표시용)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/active
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ko

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 이벤트 상세 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/1
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ko

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 이벤트 이미지 업로드 (Admin용)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/upload-image
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="event-image.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test-event-image.png
--boundary--
